  m_text: 'Now, the master will get the questions, and then you should have to answer
    them as a team. After the team''s mutual decision, the answer will be marked
    by the master. The team has to answer all the questions, i.e., 10.


    Hint:
    The team or players should not guess the answers, as there might be some questions
    that are not related to the developed methods and can heavily downgrade the overall
    score.'
